      <title>摩根士丹利和巴克莱对土耳其利率维持不变表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/morgan-stanley-barclays-in-doubt-over-turkish-rates-staying-put</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于土耳其通胀开始加速，低于预期，摩根士丹利和巴克莱银行的经济学家对于土耳其在今年剩余时间内维持利率不变产生了疑虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/morgan-stanley-barclays-in-doubt-over-turkish-rates-staying-put</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:13:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行行长表示利率稳定，通胀率达到目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/thai-central-bank-chief-signals-steady-rate-inflation-on-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行行长 Sethaput Suthiwartnarueput 表示，基准利率与政策制定者的增长和通胀前景一致，面对政府要求降息的呼声，他的立场坚定不移。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/thai-central-bank-chief-signals-steady-rate-inflation-on-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:07:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激进投资者 Cevian 入股英国 Smith & Nephew 公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/activist-investor-cevian-takes-stake-in-uk-s-smith-nephew</link>
      <description><![CDATA[激进投资者 Cevian Capital AB 披露持有 Smith &amp; Nephew Plc 5% 的股份，并将推动这家在英国上市的膝关节和髋关节置换制造商的改进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/activist-investor-cevian-takes-stake-in-uk-s-smith-nephew</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利表示购买法国股票，选举风险将消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/morgan-stanley-says-buy-french-stocks-as-election-risk-to-fade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利策略师表示，投资者应该在周日举行的第二轮提前议会选举之前买入法国股票，因为无论出现哪种最可能的结果，市场都有可能反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/morgan-stanley-says-buy-french-stocks-as-election-risk-to-fade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:29:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币因拜登闹剧和与 Mt. Gox 相关的销售风险而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/biden-flux-saps-bitcoin-alongside-risk-of-mt-gox-linked-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于面临美国政治动荡以及破产的 Mt. Gox 交易所债权人可能处置资产等挑战，比特币连续第三天下跌，接近 2 月份的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/biden-flux-saps-bitcoin-alongside-risk-of-mt-gox-linked-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 04:44:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因选举而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/asian-shares-head-for-gains-after-new-s-p-500-peak-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于关键选举成为焦点，且美国经济数据支持美联储降息理由，交易员对美联储降息理由进行了评估，欧洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/asian-shares-head-for-gains-after-new-s-p-500-peak-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 22:23:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
